        "**What is the difference between hardware and software? Give one example of each.**"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "JcVo1hle-vt7"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**Hardware** refers to the physical components of a computer, like a keyboard.\n",
        "**Software** refers to the programs that run on hardware, like Microsoft Word.\n"
      ],
